text: Ðis syndan ða landgemære into Dæglesforde.
Ærest on Bladene be westan tune and be norðan andlang ðæs sices to bægenwelle.
Of bægenwelle up to cynges ferdstræte.
Of dunemannes treowe andlang strete east to Nunnena beorge.
Of ðam beorge west to Babban beorge.
Of ðam beorge eft into Bladene be Suðantune.
